message:
added wix/react-native-navigation

downgraded react-native version to 0.51.0 since react-native-navigation still not support 0.52.0. also added typeDeclaration folder support in typescript for custom types.

updated test suite and improve project structure

using constants for screen names now for avoiding mistakes.

removed type system, added eslint

typescript was causing issues with static assets, flowtype had a lot of error with node_modules, needed to removed both of them to have a proper structure for the app

added logo to Landing screen

added Rochester font to assets for both ios and android

completed landing screen, added SkillTest and SpiceList screen

updated project structure for using global styles and constants. also added Ubuntu font family as assets

added SpiceDetail screen, updated project structure

moved screens specific components to `component` folder of each screen
